																<string>When enabled, selected power-ups are still picked up and removed, but their player-side effects are skipped. Double Damage, Cloak, and DEATH ALT timers, flags, HUD, sounds, and visual effects are not applied. This setting only affects you and bots; online opponents are not changed.</string>
